{"tid":1894412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"南韓1天增161確診 新冠肺炎累計763例、已7死","createTime":"2020-02-24T01:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T05:27:07.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a16a9bb42e7450e9ceb9ea8472caf2bbdc72b8d","tid":1894412,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"南韓中央防疫對策本部24日通報，截至當天上午9時，南韓較前一天下午4時新增161例新冠肺炎確診病例，累計確診病例達763例，出現7例死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n另據韓媒報導， 一名16個月的女嬰被確診感染，這是目前南韓年齡最小的新冠肺炎確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n南韓Kospi指數早盤大跌2.4%，新冠肺炎在南韓有爆發之虞。美國費城半導體指數上周五重挫，也讓科技股為主韓股陷於賣壓。韓元重貶0.7%至8月以來最低。<br />\n<br />\n南韓已將傳染病警報級別提高到了最高等級。南韓財政部表示，疫情意外爆發將使經濟復甦之勢受限。韓聯社報導，南韓政府將考慮一切可能選項，包括追加預算。"},{"pid":"41a4ba6428d74f330ce1a3908fdf48d93fa6fbed","tid":1894412,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/141046_99e1134788a99cfbf18b4beeefba08e6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F141046_99e1134788a99cfbf18b4beeefba08e6.gif&h=64f8b392&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b187a0c86a5fee1f96dae5a7adb8bb8db7a2ce3c","tid":1894412,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/210556_53cfaaed1c69668447f791809d5a8972.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F210556_53cfaaed1c69668447f791809d5a8972.gif&h=714dbfe2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40bfce606da63e29940385db4d80d10c4c8db566","tid":1894412,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/8a7/71e/8a771e9fc929a9c13db4f98f2e23c939bbce07f8_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F8a7%2F71e%2F8a771e9fc929a9c13db4f98f2e23c939bbce07f8_n.jpg&h=ab35f585&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a7d353555ad358c9f13384c91097dbe7ea8d98a","tid":1894412,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"韓國垃圾國家，同支那差唔多"},{"pid":"628ee4841bdefd48a2a731b9a2b663b5b68e82bf","tid":1894412,"uid":210074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"樓主on9仔"},{"pid":"a61536804eb3c18ae4e8f6c8888573b896efe482","tid":1894412,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"628ee4841bdefd48a2a731b9a2b663b5b68e82bf","tid":1894412,"uid":210074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"樓主on9仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:27:07.000Z","msg":"yes 樓主on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}